text:
Average price, $8.60 for 1 person portion. Definitely not value for money if you compare to the cai fan store beside.

Guys served me. Nothing special for their service.

Overall normal mala store. Will eat only if have craving.

Order already late. They still choose to cook the walk in order first even after I have arrived. When handing order to me. They claimed that the “foodpanda machine has no sound”. But I already saw the printed ticket hanging in their kitchen. It’s one thing to have slow service. But worse when you’re lying about it.
Fish with vegetable are very delicious. Good for single or group. Very good for famil dinner.

Their “super spicy” is not for the faint of heart!
Really good value for money
Small mala store that is underrrated. Affordable and nice! It is definitely Better than the more popular store near the MRT station.
